<item>
            <title>[LU-18221] improve check_dmesg_for_errors() to check UBSAN and KASAN errors</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18221</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We need to add checks into check_dmesg_for_errors() for UBSAN and KASAN messages in dmesg and fail the test if they are found. This would ensure we catch similar issues in the future, rather than depend on someone to see them in the test results.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
